{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSRadio","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look-and-feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note also the component must be instanciated with a string parameter used as accessibility label."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It is a good pratice (at least) to define a label for a component without text for accessibility reasons. This label will be vocalized by "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Voice Over"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The vocalization tool will also use, after the label, a description of the component (if disabled, if error context), and a fake trait for radio."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"No accessibility identifier is defined in OUDS side as this value remains in the users hands.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Cases forbidden by design","anchor":"Cases-forbidden-by-design"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error or read only situation and a disabled component.","type":"text"}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"text":"Code samples","anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading"},{"code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var selection: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A simple radio, no error, not in read only mode","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\")","","    \/\/ A simple radio, but is an error context","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true)","","    \/\/ Never disable an error-related radio button as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSRadio(isOn: $selection, accessibilityLabel: \"The cake is a lie\", isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"],"syntax":"swift","type":"codeListing"},{"text":"Design documentation","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/r.orange.fr\/r\/S-ouds-doc-radio-button"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Themes rendering","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering"},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange","anchor":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Orange"}]},{"type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Orange Compact","anchor":"Orange-Compact"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_OrangeCompact"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Sosh"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Wireframe","type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_radio_Wireframe"}]},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Version"},{"style":"note","type":"aside","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"0.12.0","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Since"}]}],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","title":"OUDSRadio","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSRadio"}],"symbolKind":"struct","platforms":[{"introducedAt":"15.0","unavailable":false,"name":"iOS","deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"macOS","introducedAt":"13.0","unavailable":false},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"tvOS","introducedAt":"16.0","unavailable":false},{"introducedAt":"1.0","unavailable":false,"name":"visionOS","deprecated":false,"beta":false},{"deprecated":false,"beta":false,"name":"watchOS","introducedAt":"11.0","unavailable":false}],"externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents9OUDSRadioV","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSRadio","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}]},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"text":"Radio button is a UI element that allows to select a single option from a set of mutually exclusive choices.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Radio button that does not show icon or text, provides greater flexibility when creating other components that require a Radio button to be displayed.","type":"text"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsradio"]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"sections":[],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/docum